# How Can You Defend The Ones You Know Are Guilty? 
That's a question I often get. People don't understand how I could possibly defend them when I know they're guilty. To be honest, that never troubled me that much. Practically speaking, it's an important consideration, but not one that ever kept me up at night. That could also be because I never had a case with a dead body, or a person who was sexually assaulted.  
